<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-12-14T07:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-12-14T07:00:00-05:00" n="524" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d524">
                                <note rend="inline" type="source">851.51/12–1447: Telegram</note>
                                <head>
                                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Caffery</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                            State</gloss>
                                    </hi>
                                </head>
                                <opener>
                                    <seg rendition="#left">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                                    </seg>
                                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                                        <placeName>
                                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-12-14T13:00:00+01:00">December 14, 1947—1 p.m.</date>
                                    </dateline>
                                </opener>
                                <p>5379. As soon as Schuman heard of the decision to grant an
                                    advance of 150 million dollars for immediate aid, he asked me to
                                    express his high appreciation thereof to the Department.</p>
                                <p>Sent Department as 5379, repeated <gloss target="#t_USDel1">USDel</gloss> London as 985.</p>
                                <closer>
                                    <signed>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Caffery</hi>
                                    </signed>
                                </closer>
                            </div>
                            </body></text></TEI>